NBHAS System Architecture

Version 1.0 (Working Draft)

1. Vision

NBHAS (Nature's Balance Health Assessment System) is a data-driven expert system designed to capture Sindi's hormone balancing expertise in a structured, maintainable, and scalable platform.

The primary goals are to:

Deliver consistent assessments.
Produce explainable recommendations.
Educate users.
Drive appropriate product recommendations.
Continuously improve using real-world assessment data.

The system must make the same decision every time when presented with identical inputs.

2. Design Philosophy

The project follows one overriding principle:

Knowledge belongs in data. Logic belongs in software. Presentation belongs in Shopify.

This separation allows:

easier maintenance
easier testing
simpler updates
future AI integration
version control of medical knowledge
