11. AI Layer (Future)

Important principle:

AI never decides.

AI explains.

Example

Rule engine determines:

Estrogen Deficiency

High

AI converts this into:

"Your responses strongly suggest..."

This keeps recommendations deterministic while making communication more natural and personalized.

12. Validation

Every build performs:

✓ duplicate IDs

✓ missing references

✓ invalid categories

✓ orphan symptoms

✓ invalid recommendation links

✓ missing resources

No JSON is generated if validation fails.

13. Versioning

Every release receives:

Knowledge Version

1.0.0

Engine Version

1.0.0

Theme Version

1.0.0

This allows you to determine exactly which knowledge base produced a particular assessment.

